{"tid":2161031,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有無巴打坐過九州啲臥鋪列車團?","createTime":"2020-08-17T10:30:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T17:04:12.000Z","uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b79b316b4b30afa28cce95d3e2e871e00df0c26f","tid":2161031,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:30:41.000Z","msg":"九州鐵路出名應該好多人都知，不過我自己唔係一個鐵膠<br />\n叫做坐過一次由布院之森咁大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但有時都會諗自己都幾鍾意九州，搵次真係試下去下啲鐵膠團當體驗下<br />\n本身無特別搵資料，係搵下屋久島啲片(呢個有plan想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)嘅時候見到呢條片<br />\n就禁嚟睇下，好似都幾過癮(雖然中間成日係架車度唔知有咩做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DO4dTbnVwKQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDO4dTbnVwKQ&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=de55a327\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DO4dTbnVwKQ</a><br />\n但一個人要戶三十萬台幣，對返港紙都成8萬蚊一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打去過啲平啲，可以分享下好唔好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n值唔值得去下<br />\n日本真係重有好多嘢做，好多地方未去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好想樣樣都體驗下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5629b98ea62158ed25efaa035d0a49e0fb6251dc","tid":2161031,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:40:06.000Z","msg":"唔值<br />\n啱時間影下相就算啦<br />\n之前搭SL人吉撞過一次, 由布院之森又遇過一次"},{"pid":"0da10db50d192b370bc87931333cc78527baee63","tid":2161031,"uid":331739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T10:42:24.000Z","msg":"8皮嘢可以由北海道玩到鹿兒島玩2個月都仲得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣坐一坐 窮人咁玩邊值<br />\n有錢佬坐完曬命就另計"},{"pid":"11fffbc8eeff3b904ac8c4bd349e56c8ff3