:37:45.000Z","msg":"影相係指影架車定中間有時間落車影風景？"},{"pid":"0dd2bd7ad7ea2ddc3b56405f1a2dee198ccb3361","tid":2161031,"uid":220355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:59:21.000Z","msg":"屋企兩老坐過 瑞風 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42a488672c80206be83ba67d6198171beedf5b4a","tid":2161031,"uid":196961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tgh1Bz8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftgh1Bz8.jpg&h=bbad0cb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我影過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e0df627562ed7160ff8c2c7e49345795dd071a4","tid":2161031,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dd2bd7ad7ea2ddc3b56405f1a2dee198ccb3361","tid":2161031,"uid":220355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T01:59:21.000Z","msg":"屋企兩老坐過 瑞風 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T09:45:26.000Z","msg":"正唔正？車上有咩做其實？"},{"pid":"3b2228a59f2fad0afd3f7abe85a7f2866b8cc115","tid":2161031,"uid":82562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"就算有錢都唔係話坐就坐<br />\n仲要抽籤, 得幾%機會中<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a41e128327a50052ecad5c4fc235e1f4730bf34","tid":2161031,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b2228a59f2fad0afd3f7abe85a7f2866b8cc115","tid":2161031,"uid":82562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T12:16:45.000Z","msg":"就算有錢都唔係話坐就坐<br />\n仲要抽籤, 得幾%機會中<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"呢個貴我都唔會去<img